From e47ad49e091a2cfb982cb771f0ab265efbb42c8d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?R=C3=A9mi=20Bernon?= <rbernon@codeweavers.com>
Date: Fri, 13 Feb 2026 23:23:45 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 03/12] ntdll: Pass thread security descriptor to new_process
 request.

---
